---
title: Cheat's Beef and Tenderstem® Biriyani with Yoghurt Drizzle and Pickled Red Onion
description: This delicious Cheat's Beef and Tenderstem® Biriyani has been expertly designed by our chefs as a lighter option to help with a balanced lifestyle.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF_Y23_R27_W23_UK_L14103-3_Main_low-76d187ef.jpg
